          Based just minutes away in Connah’s Quay, LEM Building Surveying Ltd offers independent property surveys throughout Queensferry, Shotton and the wider Deeside area. Whether you're buying your first home or assessing a rental or renovation, Liam provides reliable advice tailored to the local housing stock.
        </p>
  <h2>Our Property Survey Services</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 1 – Condition Report:</strong> Covers overall condition of newer homes, using a simple traffic-light system to flag any concerns.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 2 – HomeBuyer Report:</strong> Suitable for most conventional properties. Identifies issues, repairs and maintenance risks.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 3 – Building Survey:</strong> Full inspection and reporting for older or altered homes, including structural observations and advice.</li>
  <li><strong>Damp &amp; Timber Surveys:</strong> Investigate signs of mould, water ingress, or timber decay. Clear reporting with no pushy sales tactics.</li>
  <li><strong>Measured Surveys &amp; EPCs:</strong> Floorplans and energy certificates available for listings, planning or renovation support.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Why Clients Choose LEM</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Local &amp; Independent:</strong> No middlemen, no corporate panels — just direct communication with Liam, your surveyor.</li>
  <li><strong>AssocRICS Qualified:</strong> Professional reporting aligned with the RICS Home Survey Standard.</li>
  <li><strong>Fast Turnaround:</strong> Quotes within 60 minutes, reports usually delivered within 3–5 working days.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Serving Queensferry and Surroundings</h2>
